    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-03-23T09:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-03-23T09:00:00-05:00" n="542"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d542">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">721.23/1470: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Brazil</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morgan</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-03-23T12:00:00-02:00"
                            >March 23, 1933—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received March 23—10:50
                        a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>35. Following from Sackville received today: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“Manãos, March 18th. Leaving for front on Brazilian naval dispatch boat
                            March 17th arriving 25th. Ship has wireless apparatus. My cable address
                            American Embassy Rio de Janeiro. Cables will reach me via Brazilian Army
                            and Navy wireless stations.</p>
                        <p>Request that permission be obtained for me to enter Peruvian and
                            Colombian territory for purpose of observation and information.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>No Brazilian planes have reached the front nearer than Para.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morgan</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
